{"tid":2200884,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"借12港人被捕論去留問題遭炮轟 黃碧雲收回言論並向被捕者家屬致歉","createTime":"2020-09-13T10:29:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-13T11:14:40.000Z","uid":240362,"like":5,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"a6c5c914d9c9e1950923fda427fba0e3b172729c","tid":2200884,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T10:29:12.000Z","msg":"黃碧雲今午在Facebook發帖指，自己昨日在社交媒體上，就立法會議員去留問題及12名被內地扣押港人的相關留言，「引起了一些批評和關注」。她明白將兩件事扣連或混為一談，並不恰當，可能會令被扣押港人及其家屬感到冒犯及不安。因此她決定收回有關言論，並向家屬致深切問候，希望他們接受她摯誠的道歉。<br />\n<br />\n民主黨主席胡志偉亦在Facebook發文，就黃碧雲於社交媒體的不當言論，向被扣押港人及家屬致歉。<br />\n<br />\n胡指，今次事件關係12位被扣押港人的安危及法律權利，絕不應與其他事情相提並論，謹此代表民主黨向被扣押人士及家屬致歉。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200913/YG23X7VS2NECFBLGVBJDYVQ57I/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200913%2FYG23X7VS2NECFBLGVBJDYVQ57I%2F&d=O8bnHDCsQiwN1SoPxP513UuhYyo0AmqkWOXXUYRqYBI%3D&h=d5b1312b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200913%2FYG23X7VS2NECFBLGVBJDYVQ57I%2F&h=2683edd6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200913/YG23X7VS2NECFBLGVBJDYVQ57I/</a>"},{"pid":"36923e063b8036b1ad0843cebfd4e20b075096ac","tid":2200884,"uid":279333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T10:30:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab543004a59cb4502538028900e7a1c84f57ae36","tid":2200884,"uid":183844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T10:31:08.000Z","msg":"唉"},{"pid":"ae84f70bdeba5860ac5a1b576038e76fc075cec0","tid":2200884,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"36923e063b8036b1ad0843cebfd4e20b075096ac","tid":2200884,"uid":279333,"like":0,"disli